00:13:50,628 --> 00:13:52,463
DID YOU COME
TO THE WRONG PLACE.

208
00:13:52,463 --> 00:13:55,366
I GET THAT.

209
00:13:55,866 --> 00:13:58,703
WHY SHOULD WE BE AFRAID
OF MR. PINCUS, GARY ?

210
00:13:58,703 --> 00:14:01,489
BECAUSE HE'S A MONSTER.

211
00:14:02,490 --> 00:14:04,492
ONLY YOU CAN'T SEE THAT...

212
00:14:04,492 --> 00:14:07,278
BECAUSE HE'S CLOUDED
ALL YOUR MINDS.

213
00:14:07,278 --> 00:14:09,597
BUT HE MEANS
TO TAKE US ALL,

214
00:14:09,597 --> 00:14:11,449
ONE BY ONE.

215
00:14:11,449 --> 00:14:17,154
HARVEST OUR SOULS.
MAKE US INTO HIS ZOMBIES.

216
00:14:17,154 --> 00:14:19,690
ROBOTS MADE OUT OF MEAT.

217
00:14:19,690 --> 00:14:21,993
[ Women Sobbing ]
GOD ALMIGHTY.

218
00:14:21,993 --> 00:14:25,096
GARY, I WANT TO BELIEVE
THAT YOU'RE PROTECTING US,
BUT, UH,

219
00:14:25,096 --> 00:14:27,932
I'M KIND OF AFRAID
OF THAT RIFLE.

220
00:14:27,932 --> 00:14:32,269
IT MAKES IT HARD FOR US
ACTUAL PEOPLE TO CONCENTRATE
ON WHAT YOU'RE SAYING.

221
00:14:32,269 --> 00:14:35,656
WHY ARE YOU TALKING TO ME
LIKE I'M A THREE-YEAR-OLD ?

222
00:14:35,656 --> 00:14:39,293
DON'T ACT LIKE YOU UNDERSTAND
WHAT I'M TALKING ABOUT,

223
00:14:39,293 --> 00:14:41,295
BECAUSE YOU DON'T.

224
00:14:42,797 --> 00:14:45,599
BUT YOU WILL.

225
00:14:52,840 --> 00:14:55,843
[ Fluttering ]

226
00:14:55,843 --> 00:14:58,846
SHH !

227
00:14:58,846 --> 00:15:01,148
EVERYBODY HOLD THEIR BREATH.

228
00:15:06,871 --> 00:15:09,156
OH, YOU SONS OF BITCHES.

229
00:15:09,156 --> 00:15:11,959
OH, GARY !
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?

230
00:15:11,959 --> 00:15:14,145
- GARY ?
- [ Automatic Gunfire ]

231
00:15:14,145 --> 00:15:17,898
[ Man Over Police Radio ]
SHOTS FIRED.  SHOTS FIRED.

232
00:15:17,898 --> 00:15:20,084
EVERYBODY, HOLD YOUR FIRE !
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

233
00:15:20,084 --> 00:15:22,737
[ Man ]  HE MADE US.  HE'S
SHOOTING.  SOUNDS LIKE AN AK.
[ Gunfire Continues ]

234
00:15:22,737 --> 00:15:25,573
WE GOT TO FIND OUT
WHAT THE HELL'S GOING ON
IN THAT BUILDING.

235
00:15:25,573 --> 00:15:27,458
I'M CALLING YOUR PARTNER.
NO !

236
00:15:27,458 --> 00:15:29,760
IF IT WAS SAFE TO DO SO,
HE WOULD HAVE CALLED US
ALREADY.

237
00:15:29,760 --> 00:15:33,147
AGENT SCULLY, WE DON'T
HAVE A LOT OF OPTIONS HERE.

238
00:15:33,147 --> 00:15:35,032
[ Gunfire Continues ]

239
00:15:35,533 --> 00:15:38,502
[ People Screaming ]

240
00:15:55,202 --> 00:15:57,655
[ Cell Phone Ringing ]

241
00:16:00,024 --> 00:16:01,859
IT'S JUST MY CELL PHONE.
LET ME GET IT.

242
00:16:01,859 --> 00:16:03,978
PUT YOUR HANDS
BEHIND YOUR HEAD.

243
00:16:05,262 --> 00:16:08,099
[ Ringing ]

244
00:16:13,971 --> 00:16:16,924
[ Ringing Continues ]

245
00:16:30,421 --> 00:16:33,557
[ Ringing Continues ]

246
00:16:44,568 --> 00:16:47,872
[ Ringing Continues ]

247
00:16:52,009 --> 00:16:55,362
F.B.I. ?
YOU HAPPY NOW ?

248
00:16:57,097 --> 00:16:59,216
HUH ?  YOU WANT TO
MESS WITH ME SOME MORE ?

249
00:17:02,903 --> 00:17:06,474
[ Rice ]
HELLO ?  HELLO ?
IS ANYBODY ON THE LINE ?

250
00:17:06,474 --> 00:17:08,759
WE HEARD GUNFIRE.
IS EVERYONE ALL RIGHT ?

251
00:17:08,759 --> 00:17:11,111
I JUST SHOT A ZOMBIE.

252
00:17:11,612 --> 00:17:13,364
EVERYBODY THINKS I KILLED HIM,
BUT I DIDN'T.

253
00:17:13,364 --> 00:17:17,134
- WHO AM I SPEAKING TO ?
- THE GUY THAT'S GONNA START
  KILLING ACTUAL PEOPLE...

254
00:17:17,134 --> 00:17:20,104
IF YOU DON'T PUT ME
ON THE DAMN TV !

255
00:17:20,104 --> 00:17:23,641
I THINK HE JUST SHOT
A HOSTAGE.
WHO ?

256
00:17:23,641 --> 00:17:26,010
HE'S STILL ASKING FOR
HIS 15 MINUTES OF FAME.

257
00:17:28,846 --> 00:17:30,681
GIVE IT TO HIM.

258
00:17:30,681 --> 00:17:34,084
GET IT OUT OF SIGHT.

259
00:17:37,104 --> 00:17:39,823
YOU WANT TO KNOW WHY
IT JUMPED AT ME LIKE THAT ?

260
00:17:39,823 --> 00:17:41,892
IT'S NOT AN "IT," GARY.

261
00:17:41,892 --> 00:17:43,894
IT'S A "HE."
 IT'S A MAN YOU JUST KILLED.

262
00:17:46,813 --> 00:17:49,233
- WHAT WAS HIS NAME ?
- MARK BACKUS.

263
00:17:49,233 --> 00:17:51,218
WRONG !

264
00:17:51,718 --> 00:17:54,221
IT STOPPED BEING MARK BACKUS
WHEN HE TURNED IT
INTO A ZOMBIE.

265
00:17:54,221 --> 00:17:59,243
AND THEN HE INSTRUCTED IT
BY MEANS OF MENTAL TELEPATHY
TO ATTACK ME.

266
00:18:03,580 --> 00:18:06,016
AND SO I SHOT IT.

267
00:18:06,016 --> 00:18:08,268
I HAD NO CHOICE.

268
00:18:10,637 --> 00:18:13,390
BUT IT DOESN'T MATTER,
BECAUSE IT WAS ALREADY DEAD.

269
00:18:13,390 --> 00:18:16,226
HE WANTS US ALL LIKE THAT.

270
00:18:16,727 --> 00:18:19,012
INSECTS, NOT PEOPLE.

271
00:18:19,012 --> 00:18:22,416
MINDLESS DRONES.

272
00:18:22,916 --> 00:18:25,419
HE WANTS TO TAKE AWAY
WHO WE ARE.

273
00:18:26,820 --> 00:18:29,823
TO CONTROL US,

274
00:18:29,823 --> 00:18:32,326
SO WE'LL BE
HIS EYES AND EARS...

275
00:18:32,326 --> 00:18:35,329
AND SPY ON EACH OTHER
 AND HELP HIM DO HIS DIRTY WORK.

276
00:18:35,829 --> 00:18:40,167
GARY, IF I'M THE MONSTER,

277
00:18:40,167 --> 00:18:42,419
WHAT DO YOU NEED
THESE PEOPLE FOR ?

278
00:18:44,771 --> 00:18:47,541
WHY DON'T YOU JUST
LET 'EM ALL GO ?

279
00:18:47,541 --> 00:18:52,012
YOU JUST WAIT TILL
I PUT YOU ON TV.

280
00:18:52,012 --> 00:18:54,081
THEN THEY'LL SEE
WHAT YOU ARE.

281
00:18:56,583 --> 00:18:59,086
[ Cell Phone Ringing ]

282
00:19:00,837 --> 00:19:03,907
ANSWER THE PHONE, GARY.

283
00:19:05,909 --> 00:19:08,412
[ Ringing ]

284
00:19:08,412 --> 00:19:10,781
DIAL AND SMILE.

285
00:19:11,281 --> 00:19:14,051
[ Rice ]  OKAY.  WE'RE
SENDING YOU THE CAMERAMAN
NOW.  JUST STAY CALM.

286
00:19:14,051 --> 00:19:17,054
FINALLY.
LET'S DO IT.

287
00:19:18,972 --> 00:19:20,841
[ Phone Beeps ]

288
00:19:20,841 --> 00:19:23,944
WARREN, THAT IS EXACTLY
WHAT WE'RE HEARING.

289
00:19:23,944 --> 00:19:29,232
ALL YOU PEOPLE PUT YOUR
BUTTS AGAINST THE DOOR.
HURRY IT UP.  GO !

290
00:19:29,232 --> 00:19:32,152
YOU.  GET OVER BY
THE CAMERA.  MOVE IT !

291
00:19:32,152 --> 00:19:34,554
...MOMENTARILY TO
AN ACTUAL LIVE FEED--

292
00:19:34,554 --> 00:19:39,309
THIS PERSON OR PEOPLE MAY HAVE
SOMETHING IMPORTANT TO SAY.

293
00:19:39,309 --> 00:19:43,013
SEE WHO'S GETTING HURT
IF YOU BUST DOWN THIS DOOR ?

294
00:19:43,013 --> 00:19:45,849
APPARENTLY,
SO FAR THERE'S BEEN
VERY LITTLE COMMUNICATION...

295
00:19:45,849 --> 00:19:49,336
- BETWEEN THE POLICE AND THE
  PEOPLE INSIDE THE BUILDING.
- IS HE GETTING THIS ?

296
00:19:49,336 --> 00:19:52,122
YEAH.  CLOSED CIRCUIT IS
BOUNCING IT RIGHT BACK
INTO THE BUILDING.

297
00:19:52,122 --> 00:19:54,324
HE THINKS
HE'S GONNA BE A STAR.

298
00:19:54,324 --> 00:19:56,493
ALL RIGHT.
SHOW US THE ROOM.

299
00:19:56,493 --> 00:20:00,313
[ Gary ]  WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?
[ Man ]  HOLD ON.
MY BATTERY CABLE'S TWISTED.

300
00:20:00,313 --> 00:20:03,817
WELL, UNTWIST IT !
AND HURRY THE HELL UP !

301
00:20:03,817 --> 00:20:06,103
THERE !  RIGHT THERE !
THE EXTERIOR WALL'S CLEAR.

302
00:20:06,103 --> 00:20:08,071
ENTRY TEAM
INTO POSITION.

303
00:20:14,528 --> 00:20:16,813
LIE DOWN ON THE FLOOR.

304
00:20:17,314 --> 00:20:19,716
DO IT !

305
00:20:21,668 --> 00:20:24,971
[ Newswoman Chattering ]
ALL RIGHT.
PUT ME ON.

306
00:20:26,306 --> 00:20:28,108
OKAY.
WE'RE GONNA CUT INSIDE.

307
00:20:28,108 --> 00:20:30,861
YES, HERE IT IS.
HERE WE GO.

308
00:20:32,279 --> 00:20:34,197
[ Clears Throat ]

309
00:20:37,784 --> 00:20:40,787
PEOPLE OF AMERICA,

310
00:20:40,787 --> 00:20:43,623
A MONSTER WALKS AMONG YOU.

311
00:20:43,623 --> 00:20:45,492
GO, PAN OVER.

312
00:20:48,712 --> 00:20:51,164
GET UP.

313
00:21:00,857 --> 00:21:04,478
- NOW I'LL SHOW IT TO YOU.
- NO, GARY.

314
00:21:04,478 --> 00:21:07,330
- GET OUT OF THE WAY.
- DON'T DO THIS.

315
00:21:07,330 --> 00:21:10,016
GET OUT OF THE WAY.

316
00:21:10,016 --> 00:21:12,102
DON'T DO THIS, GARY.

317
00:21:14,071 --> 00:21:16,406
- GET OUT OF THE WAY !
- PUT DOWN THE RIFLE.

318
00:21:16,406 --> 00:21:19,976
GET OUT OF THE WAY NOW !

319
00:21:22,896 --> 00:21:25,398
[ Fluttering ]

320
00:21:25,398 --> 00:21:27,400
THERE !

321
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:30,220
LOOK AT IT !

322
00:21:30,720 --> 00:21:33,690
LOOK AT IT !

323
00:21:44,751 --> 00:21:46,470
SEE ?

324
00:21:48,789 --> 00:21:51,691
[ Rumbling ]

325
00:22:02,619 --> 00:22:05,288
[ Shot Fires ]
[ Groans ]

326
00:22:05,288 --> 00:22:07,073
[ Women Screaming ]

327
00:22:13,213 --> 00:22:15,715
[ Men Shouting ]

328
00:22:37,220 --> 00:22:40,223
[ Man ]
LINE UP AGAINST THE WALL !

329
00:22:45,011 --> 00:22:47,514
NOW YOU KNOW.

330
00:23:04,581 --> 00:23:06,633
[ Woman Over Police Radio,
  Indistinct ]

331
00:23:08,135 --> 00:23:10,137
[ People Chattering ]

332
00:23:15,559 --> 00:23:18,095
YOU LOOK EXHAUSTED.
NO, I'M FINE.

333
00:23:18,095 --> 00:23:21,565
AGENT RICE HAS
THE SITUATION IN HAND.
LET'S GET YOU OUT OF HERE.

334
00:23:27,738 --> 00:23:29,740
MULDER ?

335
00:23:34,378 --> 00:23:36,380
I CAN'T BEGIN
TO THANK YOU.

336
00:23:36,880 --> 00:23:38,882
I OWE YOU MY LIFE.
WE ALL DO.

337
00:23:40,384 --> 00:23:43,904
DO YOU HAVE ANY IDEA
WHY HE FIXATED ON YOU
THE WAY HE DID ?

338
00:23:44,404 --> 00:23:45,906
NO.
NOT AT ALL.

339
00:23:46,406 --> 00:23:48,909
I FEEL LIKE I BARELY
EVEN KNEW THE MAN.

340
00:23:48,909 --> 00:23:51,061
I MEAN, I TRY TO BE
A GOOD GUY TO WORK FOR.

341
00:23:51,562 --> 00:23:54,064
YOU MENTIONED ANOTHER INCIDENT
WITH ANOTHER EMPLOYEE...

342
00:23:54,064 --> 00:23:56,767
AT A PLANT IN KANSAS CITY
IN 1994 ?

343
00:23:56,767 --> 00:24:00,504
- YES.
- WERE YOU AT THAT PLANT
  AT THAT TIME ?

344
00:24:00,504 --> 00:24:03,190
I WASN'T THERE
WHEN IT HAPPENED,
BUT YEAH.

345
00:24:03,190 --> 00:24:05,275
DIDN'T I MENTION THAT ?

346
00:24:05,275 --> 00:24:08,395
WHAT ABOUT LAKELAND, FLORIDA ?
HAVE YOU EVER LIVED THERE ?

347
00:24:09,846 --> 00:24:12,099
I'VE BEEN THERE.
I HAVE RELATIVES THERE.

348
00:24:13,684 --> 00:24:17,087
IS THERE ANYTHING ELSE ?

349
00:24:17,087 --> 00:24:20,591
UH, NO, MR. PINCUS.
THANK YOU VERY MUCH
FOR YOUR PATIENCE.

350
00:24:23,360 --> 00:24:25,362
WHAT'S GOING ON ?

351
00:24:26,863 --> 00:24:28,865
I DON'T KNOW.

352
00:24:53,557 --> 00:24:55,058
[ Door Opens ]

353
00:24:57,010 --> 00:24:59,863
- MULDER, WHY DIDN'T YOU
  TAKE THE DAY OFF ?
- CLOSE THE DOOR.

354
00:25:02,582 --> 00:25:06,036
THERE WAS A REASON THE PHRASE
"HIDING IN THE LIGHT" SEEMED
SO FAMILIAR TO ME.

355
00:25:06,536 --> 00:25:09,539
I FOUND IT OR VARIATIONS
OF IT IN FIVE OTHER X-FILES.

356
00:25:09,539 --> 00:25:12,943
"HIDING IN PLAIN VIEW,"
"HIDING IN THE OPEN,"
"LURKING IN THE OPEN"--

357
00:25:12,943 --> 00:25:15,829
ALL TO DESCRIBE SOME
MANIFESTATION OF EVIL...

358
00:25:15,829 --> 00:25:19,166
WHICH GOES UNNOTICED
BY EVERYONE EXCEPT
THE CLAIMANT IN EACH CASE.

359
00:25:19,166 --> 00:25:22,402
HAVE YOU SLEPT ?
SEVEN CITIES IN ALL,
DATING BACK TEN YEARS.

360
00:25:22,402 --> 00:25:25,906
VINYLRIGHT HAS OFFICES
WITHIN 50 MILES
OF FOUR OF THOSE CITIES.

361
00:25:26,406 --> 00:25:29,543
GREG PINCUS HAS WORKED
FOR VINYLRIGHT FOR
GUESS FOR HOW LONG ?

362
00:25:29,543 --> 00:25:32,546
TEN YEARS.
WHAT EXACTLY IS IT THAT
YOU THINK YOU HAVE HERE ?

363
00:25:32,546 --> 00:25:36,266
WHAT IF GARY LAMBERT
WAS RIGHT ?

364
00:25:36,767 --> 00:25:39,086
- MULDER, YOU'RE NOT SERIOUS.
- JUST BEAR WITH ME
  FOR A MOMENT.

365
00:25:39,086 --> 00:25:42,089
I MEAN, WHAT IF SUCH
A CREATURE EXISTED THAT
COULD CAMOUFLAGE ITSELF...

366
00:25:42,089 --> 00:25:43,840
BY CLOUDING THE MINDS
OF ITS VICTIMS ?

367
00:25:43,840 --> 00:25:46,093
THERE ARE ANTECEDENTS
FOR IT IN NATURE
RIGHT IN THE INSECT WORLD.

368
00:25:46,093 --> 00:25:49,346
MANTIS, FOR INSTANCE.
THEY'RE SAID TO BE ABLE
TO HYPNOTIZE THEIR PREY.

369
00:25:49,346 --> 00:25:53,133
NO.
WHAT IF IT COULD INDUCE
A VISUAL HALLUCINATION ?

370
00:25:53,133 --> 00:25:56,887
A SORT OF TEMPORARY
CONVERSION DISORDER ?

371
00:25:58,205 --> 00:26:01,908
WHAT YOU'RE DESCRIBING
WOULD BE MORE LIKE
SOME KIND OF...

372
00:26:01,908 --> 00:26:03,910
VISUAL AGNOSIA,

373
00:26:03,910 --> 00:26:06,713
AN INABILITY TO RECOGNIZE
WHAT'S BEFORE ONE'S EYES.

374
00:26:06,713 --> 00:26:09,516
ONLY GARY LAMBERT COULD
SEE THROUGH IT SOMEHOW,
AS COULD THE OTHERS.

375
00:26:09,516 --> 00:26:12,019
MAYBE BECAUSE OF SOME
HEIGHTENED ADRENALINE LEVEL,

376
00:26:12,019 --> 00:26:14,404
OR MAYBE JUST BECAUSE HE KNEW
WHERE TO LOOK SOMEHOW.

377
00:26:14,404 --> 00:26:19,009
MULDER, HE WAS DISTURBED.
YEAH, BUT DID HE SEE IT
BECAUSE HE WAS DISTURBED,

378
00:26:19,009 --> 00:26:21,011
OR WAS HE DISTURBED
BECAUSE HE SAW IT ?

379
00:26:21,011 --> 00:26:23,397
HE WAS MENTALLY ILL.

380
00:26:23,397 --> 00:26:25,399
THIS MONSTER WAS A--
WAS A SICK FANTASY,

381
00:26:25,399 --> 00:26:27,284
A PRODUCT
OF HIS DEMENTIA.

382
00:26:28,785 --> 00:26:30,787
I SAW IT TOO.

383
00:26:32,189 --> 00:26:34,474
DOES THAT MAKE ME DISTURBED ?

384
00:26:34,474 --> 00:26:38,478
DEMENTED ?  DOES THAT
MAKE ME SICK TOO ?

385
00:26:40,914 --> 00:26:42,916
NO.

386
00:26:42,916 --> 00:26:45,786
NO, I MEAN, THIS KIND
OF THING IS NOT UNCOMMON.

387
00:26:45,786 --> 00:26:49,406
YOU--  YOU WENT THROUGH
A TERRIBLE ORDEAL.

388
00:26:49,406 --> 00:26:52,242
AND SOMETIMES PEOPLE
IN CLOSE ASSOCIATIONS...

389
00:26:52,242 --> 00:26:55,128
UNDER TENSE CONDITIONS
CAN--

390
00:26:55,128 --> 00:26:57,464
THE DELUSIONS OF ONE
CAN BE PASSED ON
TO THE OTHER.

391
00:26:57,464 --> 00:26:59,366
FOLIE A DEUX ?

392
00:26:59,866 --> 00:27:01,868
IT'S NOT THAT, SCULLY.
IT'S NOT
HELSINKI SYNDROME EITHER.

393
00:27:01,868 --> 00:27:04,371
WHAT I SAW WAS REAL,
AND THERE MAY BE A WAY
TO PROVE IT.

394
00:27:04,371 --> 00:27:06,556
HOW ?

395
00:27:06,556 --> 00:27:10,360
LAMBERT POINTED OUT
CERTAIN INDIVIDUALS HE SAID
HAD BEEN VICTIMIZED BY PINCUS.

396
00:27:10,360 --> 00:27:13,363
TURNED INTO ZOMBIES.
THE MAN HE SHOT, BACKUS,
WAS ONE OF THEM.

397
00:27:13,363 --> 00:27:16,216
IF YOU COULD AUTOPSY
THE BODY--
NO.  NO, ABSOLUTELY NOT.

398
00:27:16,216 --> 00:27:18,718
SCULLY, IF THIS IS
ALL IN MY MIND,
AS YOU SAY IT IS,

399
00:27:18,718 --> 00:27:21,054
I WOULD BE VERY GRATEFUL
IF YOU WOULD PROVE THAT.

400
00:27:21,054 --> 00:27:23,974
MULDER, I AM NOT GOING
TO SERVE THE DELUSIONS
OF GARY LAMBERT,

401
00:27:24,474 --> 00:27:27,727
A MADMAN, BY GIVING
CREDENCE TO THEM.

402
00:27:28,879 --> 00:27:31,131
THEN I'LL PROVE IT
WITHOUT YOU.

403
00:27:33,984 --> 00:27:35,652
MULDER--

404
00:27:43,660 --> 00:27:46,663
[ Rice ]
WHAT ARE WE LOOKING FOR ?
I'LL KNOW IT WHEN I SEE IT.

405
00:28:01,261 --> 00:28:03,263
WHAT'S THIS ABOUT ?

406
00:28:03,263 --> 00:28:05,765
LAMBERT WAS TRACKING
HIS BOSS'S MOVEMENTS
OVER THE YEARS.

407
00:28:05,765 --> 00:28:09,269
STALKING HIM.
GATHERING EVIDENCE.

408
00:28:24,633 --> 00:28:26,469
WHAT IS IT ?

409
00:28:35,311 --> 00:28:37,313
DID YOU SEE HER ?
 DID YOU SEE WHERE SHE WENT ?
WHO ?

410
00:28:39,315 --> 00:28:42,151
YOU MIND TELLING ME
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE ?
[ Car Engine Starting ]

411
00:29:00,319 --> 00:29:02,321
SIR ?

412
00:29:02,321 --> 00:29:05,474
YOU WANTED TO SEE ME ?

413
00:29:05,474 --> 00:29:09,311
YES, I WAS HOPING YOU COULD
GIVE ME SOME INSIGHT INTO
AGENT MULDER'S RECENT BEHAVIOR.

414
00:29:09,311 --> 00:29:11,614
SIR ?

415
00:29:12,114 --> 00:29:14,116
WHY IS HE BACK
IN ILLINOIS ?

416
00:29:14,116 --> 00:29:16,118
I THOUGHT THAT CASE
WAS CLOSED.

417
00:29:17,620 --> 00:29:19,622
AGENT MULDER BELIEVES THAT
THERE MAY BE A CONNECTION...

418
00:29:20,122 --> 00:29:22,875
BETWEEN THE OAK BROOK
INCIDENT AND SEVERAL
OTHER CASES.

419
00:29:22,875 --> 00:29:24,910
BUT YOU ELECTED
NOT TO JOIN HIM.

420
00:29:24,910 --> 00:29:26,962
THE CHICAGO FIELD OFFICE
HAS BEEN IN CONTACT WITH HIM.

421
00:29:26,962 --> 00:29:29,732
THEY DESCRIBE HIS BEHAVIOR
AS BEING ERRATIC.

422
00:29:31,667 --> 00:29:34,170
TO THE BEST OF MY
KNOWLEDGE, AGENT MULDER
IS CURRENTLY WORKING...

423
00:29:34,170 --> 00:29:37,173
ON A LEGITIMATE
INVESTIGATION.

424
00:29:37,173 --> 00:29:39,175
I WILL JOIN HIM
IN ILLINOIS IMMEDIATELY.

425
00:29:39,175 --> 00:29:42,628
DON'T YOU HAVE AN AUTOPSY
TO DO FIRST ?

426
00:29:43,129 --> 00:29:45,631
THIS BODY
MULDER SENT TO QUANTICO.

427
00:29:47,133 --> 00:29:49,952
MARK BACKUS,
THE SHOOTING VICTIM.

428
00:29:49,952 --> 00:29:53,305
YOU'RE SCHEDULED TO DO
AN EXAMINATION.

429
00:29:53,305 --> 00:29:57,476
- OR DIDN'T YOU KNOW THAT ?
- I'LL GET RIGHT ON IT, SIR.

430
00:29:58,978 --> 00:30:02,481
IS THERE SOMETHING
YOU WANT TO TELL ME, SCULLY ?

431
00:30:02,982 --> 00:30:04,483
NO, SIR.

432
00:30:05,484 --> 00:30:07,937
[ Door Opens, Shuts ]

433
00:30:10,840 --> 00:30:12,625
[ Scully ]
LET'S START WITH THE PHOTOS.

434
00:30:12,625 --> 00:30:14,693
IN FACT,
LET'S JUST DO PHOTOS.

435
00:30:14,693 --> 00:30:17,646
EXTERNAL EXAM ONLY.

436
00:30:17,646 --> 00:30:20,416
THIS GUY CAME AN AWFUL
LONG WAY JUST TO HAVE
HIS PICTURE TAKEN.

437
00:30:20,850 --> 00:30:23,135
KNOCK YOURSELF OUT.

438
00:30:23,135 --> 00:30:26,138
CASE NUMBER 986522.

439
00:30:26,138 --> 00:30:29,892
MARK BACKUS,
45-YEAR-OLD CAUCASIAN MALE.
[ Ringing ]

440
00:30:30,259 --> 00:30:33,262
THERE ARE THREE
ONE-CENTIMETER
GUNSHOT ENTRY WOUNDS...

441
00:30:33,262 --> 00:30:36,048
ON THE LEFT
ANTERIOR CHEST WALL...

442
00:30:36,048 --> 00:30:37,883
- WITH SOME BURN
  STIPPLING PRESENT.
- COME ON, MULDER.

443
00:30:38,384 --> 00:30:40,886
JUDGING FROM THE CORPSE'S
RESOLVED RIGOR
AND FIXED LIVIDITY,

444
00:30:41,387 --> 00:30:42,888
AS WELL AS THE
DECOMPOSITIONAL BLOATING,

445
00:30:43,389 --> 00:30:45,991
I'D PLACE THE TIME OF DEATH
BETWEEN 48 AND 72 HOURS.

446
00:30:45,991 --> 00:30:48,761
NO.

447
00:30:48,761 --> 00:30:50,596
THIS MAN DIED
LATE YESTERDAY AFTERNOON.

448
00:30:50,596 --> 00:30:53,532
ARE YOU SURE ?
ABSOLUTELY.

449
00:30:53,532 --> 00:30:57,319
IT SURE LOOKS TO ME
LIKE HE'S BEEN DEAD
LONGER THAN THAT.

450
00:31:45,184 --> 00:31:48,520
[ Man On TV,
  Indistinct ]

451
00:31:57,379 --> 00:32:00,749
dddd [ Man Singing ]

452
00:32:02,585 --> 00:32:04,753
[ Fluttering ]

453
00:32:08,807 --> 00:32:11,076
[ Woman Screams ]

454
00:32:32,014 --> 00:32:34,700
[ Girl On TV ]
I WANT TO DO THAT TOO.

455
00:32:34,700 --> 00:32:37,202
[ People On TV Continue,
  Indistinct ]

456
00:32:54,153 --> 00:32:56,538
[ Clattering ]

457
00:33:10,334 --> 00:33:14,338
SUDDENLY I BECAME AWARE
OF THIS... PRESENCE.

458
00:33:15,840 --> 00:33:18,843
AND I COULD FEEL IT
CREEPING TOWARD ME.

459
00:33:19,343 --> 00:33:21,345
IT WAS TERRIFYING.

460
00:33:21,846 --> 00:33:24,982
THE NEXT THING I KNEW,
THIS MADMAN'S INSIDE MY HOUSE.

461
00:33:24,982 --> 00:33:27,268
HE BREAKS MY WINDOW,
KICKS IN THE DOOR,

462
00:33:27,268 --> 00:33:31,138
AND THE WHOLE TIME
HE'S SCREAMING ABOUT MONSTERS--
I MEAN, EVEN WORSE THAN GARY.

463
00:33:36,277 --> 00:33:39,280
MISS STARNS,
I APOLOGIZE FOR THIS INCIDENT.

464
00:33:39,280 --> 00:33:43,067
I ASSURE YOU IT WILL RECEIVE
MY UTMOST ATTENTION.

465
00:33:46,404 --> 00:33:49,407
WHY DON'T YOU TAKE THE REST
OF THE WEEK, GRETCHEN ?
THANK YOU, MR. PINCUS.

466
00:33:53,978 --> 00:33:56,981
THAT MAN HAS NO BUSINESS
CARRYING A GUN, IF YOU ASK ME.

467
00:34:10,645 --> 00:34:13,264
- YOU GOT TO HER, TOO,
  DIDN'T YOU ?
- AGENT MULDER--

468
00:34:13,264 --> 00:34:16,701
I WAS TOO LATE.
YOU CHANGED HER SOMEHOW.
YOU INFECTED HER.

469
00:34:16,701 --> 00:34:21,789
AGENT MULDER, THINK VERY
CAREFULLY ABOUT THE NEXT WORDS
THAT COME OUT OF YOUR MOUTH.

470
00:34:21,789 --> 00:34:25,443
ONCE AGAIN, I APOLOGIZE.

471
00:34:25,443 --> 00:34:29,447
OH, THERE'S NO NEED.
I'M WELL AWARE OF THE STRESS
AGENT MULDER'S BEEN UNDER,

472
00:34:29,947 --> 00:34:32,366
AND I'M, UH--
WELL, I STILL CONSIDER
HIM A HERO.

473
00:34:32,366 --> 00:34:35,169
WHICH IS WHY I WANT TO
HANDLE THIS PRIVATELY.

474
00:34:35,169 --> 00:34:37,555
WE APPRECIATE THAT.

475
00:34:37,555 --> 00:34:40,891
FOR MY PART, I'M HAPPY TO LET
THIS ENTIRE MATTER DROP.

476
00:34:40,891 --> 00:34:43,811
I'M SURE I CAN PERSUADE
MISS STARNS TO DO THE SAME,

477
00:34:43,811 --> 00:34:46,147
PROVIDED AGENT MULDER
IS AMENABLE.

478
00:34:46,147 --> 00:34:48,783
YOU DON'T SEE
WHAT'S GOING ON HERE.

479
00:34:48,783 --> 00:34:50,935
I'M AFRAID I DO.

480
00:34:50,935 --> 00:34:53,788
LAMBERT KNEW YOUR SECRET.
HE KNEW YOU WERE SUCKING
THE HUMANITY...

481
00:34:53,788 --> 00:34:55,573
OUT OF THESE PEOPLE,
FEEDING ON THEM.

482
00:34:55,573 --> 00:34:58,693
AGENT MULDER, THAT'S ENOUGH.
I DON'T WANT TO HEAR
ANOTHER WORD OUT OF YOU.

483
00:34:58,693 --> 00:35:01,946
IF YOU CARE ABOUT YOUR CAREER,
THEN YOU'LL KNOCK THIS CRAP OFF.
[ Creaking ]

484
00:35:02,446 --> 00:35:05,449
BECAUSE I GUARANTEE I WILL NOT
STAND FOR ANOTHER SECOND
OF THIS ABUSE.

485
00:35:05,449 --> 00:35:07,401
DO YOU UNDERSTAND ME--
[ No Audible Dialogue ]

486
00:35:07,401 --> 00:35:09,637
[ Creaking Continues ]

487
00:35:09,637 --> 00:35:13,541
GET OUT OF THE WAY !
 GET OUT OF HERE !
NO !  STOP IT !

488
00:35:13,541 --> 00:35:15,743
LOOK AT HIM !
 LOOK AT HIM !

489
00:35:15,743 --> 00:35:17,528
[ Shouts ]

490
00:35:23,484 --> 00:35:26,804
STOP IT.

491
00:35:40,284 --> 00:35:42,169
[ Mulder ]
FIVE YEARS TOGETHER, SCULLY.

492
00:35:42,169 --> 00:35:45,639
YOU MUST HAVE
SEEN THIS COMING.

493
00:35:47,641 --> 00:35:49,927
DID YOU EXAMINE
BACKUS'S BODY ?

494
00:35:51,228 --> 00:35:54,231
WHAT DID YOU FIND ?

495
00:35:54,231 --> 00:35:56,567
MORE OR LESS WHAT
WE THOUGHT WE'D FIND.

496
00:35:56,567 --> 00:35:59,220
MORE OR LESS ?
WHAT IS THAT
SUPPOSED TO MEAN ?

497
00:36:01,071 --> 00:36:04,909
THE BODY SHOWED SIGNS
OF DECOMPOSITION BEYOND
WHAT WE EXPECTED TO FIND.

498
00:36:04,909 --> 00:36:10,531
WHICH IN AND OF ITSELF
MEANS NOTHING, REALLY.

499
00:36:10,531 --> 00:36:13,334
TIME OF DEATH
IS NOTORIOUSLY HARD
TO QUANTIFY.

500
00:36:13,334 --> 00:36:17,054
OR THAT LAMBERT WAS TELLING
THE TRUTH, AND THAT MAN WAS DEAD
BEFORE HE WAS GUNNED DOWN.

501
00:36:17,054 --> 00:36:21,675
NO, MULDER.
SCULLY,
WHEN THAT MONSTER,

502
00:36:21,675 --> 00:36:23,994
PINCUS, WHATEVER THE HELL
YOU WANT TO CALL IT,

503
00:36:23,994 --> 00:36:26,997
WHEN HE ATTACKED THAT WOMAN
LAST NIGHT, HE DID SOMETHING
TO THE BACK OF HER NECK.

504
00:36:26,997 --> 00:36:30,000
HE BIT HER THERE,
OR HE INJECTED
SOMETHING IN THERE.

505
00:36:30,000 --> 00:36:32,286
THERE'S GOT TO BE
EVIDENCE OF THAT.
YOU GOTTA CHECK FOR THAT.

506
00:36:32,286 --> 00:36:34,638
MULDER,
THE CASE IS OVER.

507
00:36:34,638 --> 00:36:37,641
THERE'S NO MORE EVIDENCE
TO BE GATHERED.

508
00:36:39,610 --> 00:36:42,997
THERE'S ONLY MY HOPE
THAT YOU'LL BE ABLE TO
SEE PAST THIS DELUSION.

509
00:36:44,899 --> 00:36:48,652
YOU... HAVE TO
BE WILLING TO SEE.

510
00:36:50,421 --> 00:36:52,790
I WISH IT WERE
THAT SIMPLE.

511
00:36:52,790 --> 00:36:56,760
SCULLY, YOU HAVE TO
BELIEVE ME.

512
00:36:56,760 --> 00:37:00,764
NOBODY ELSE ON THIS
WHOLE DAMN PLANET
DOES OR EVER WILL.

513
00:37:02,950 --> 00:37:05,953
YOU'RE MY ONE
IN FIVE BILLION.

514
00:37:14,278 --> 00:37:16,280
WELL, YOU JUST MADE IT.
I WAS ABOUT TO SHIP HIM.

515
00:37:16,780 --> 00:37:18,666
[ Zipper Unzips ]

516
00:37:23,787 --> 00:37:27,291
FULL AUTOPSY THIS TIME ?
NO.  LET'S FLIP HIM.

517
00:37:27,291 --> 00:37:29,793
FLIP HIM OVER ?
YEP.

518
00:37:30,294 --> 00:37:32,296
GIVE ME A HAND.

519
00:38:18,859 --> 00:38:20,778
WE CAN DO WITHOUT THESE, HUH ?
WHAT DO YOU SAY ?

520
00:38:20,778 --> 00:38:22,897
SORRY.

521
00:38:29,954 --> 00:38:31,739
[ Nurse ]
THERE WE GO.

522
00:38:38,212 --> 00:38:40,214
SLEEP TIGHT.

523
00:38:40,714 --> 00:38:42,716
DON'T LET
THE BEDBUGS BITE.

524
00:38:45,135 --> 00:38:47,888
[ Door Shuts ]

525
00:39:03,704 --> 00:39:06,206
[ Tapping At Window ]

526
00:39:06,707 --> 00:39:08,709
[ Fluttering ]

527
00:39:15,916 --> 00:39:18,135
[ Gasps ]

528
00:39:18,135 --> 00:39:20,604
NURSE !

529
00:39:20,604 --> 00:39:22,556
NURSE !

530
00:39:22,556 --> 00:39:24,674
NURSE !

531
00:39:24,674 --> 00:39:26,860
IT'S HERE !

532
00:39:26,860 --> 00:39:29,746
NURSE !  IT'S HERE !

533
00:39:29,746 --> 00:39:31,915
IT'S HERE !
 IT'S AT THE WINDOW !

534
00:39:31,915 --> 00:39:35,202
- WHAT'S HERE ?
- THERE IS SOMETHING--

535
00:39:35,202 --> 00:39:38,205
THERE IS SOMETHING
AT THE WINDOW,
AND IT'S TRYING TO GET IN HERE.

536
00:39:38,205 --> 00:39:41,007
PLEASE UNSTRAP ME
SO THAT I CAN STOP IT.
SIR--

537
00:39:41,007 --> 00:39:43,276
SIR, WE'RE THREE FLOORS UP.
THERE'S NOTHING AT THE WINDOW.

538
00:39:43,276 --> 00:39:46,746
JUST... UN-UNDO MY STRAPS
SO THAT I CAN CHECK.

539
00:39:46,746 --> 00:39:49,633
I CAN SHOW YOU--
NO, DON'T !  NO !
JUST, PLEASE--

540
00:39:49,633 --> 00:39:51,751
PLEASE.

541
00:39:56,273 --> 00:40:00,093
SEE ?  NOTHING'S
GONNA GET YOU.

542
00:40:00,093 --> 00:40:02,045
OKAY.  JUST, UH--

543
00:40:02,546 --> 00:40:04,981
JUST UNTIE ME ANYWAY,
PLEASE.

544
00:40:14,257 --> 00:40:16,543
WHAT ARE YOU DOING ?

545
00:40:16,543 --> 00:40:18,812
YOU JUST NEED
SOME FRESH AIR.

546
00:40:36,746 --> 00:40:39,666
I CAN'T BE RUNNING IN HERE
ALL NIGHT, OKAY ?

547
00:40:43,787 --> 00:40:45,589
[ Door Shuts ]

548
00:40:49,976 --> 00:40:52,979
[ Fluttering ]

549
00:41:03,506 --> 00:41:06,026
[ Gasping ]

550
00:41:19,005 --> 00:41:22,342
HELP !
SOMEBODY HELP !

551
00:41:22,342 --> 00:41:26,196
VERY SORRY,
BUT IT IS AFTER HOURS,
AND MR. MULDER IS RESTING.

552
00:41:26,196 --> 00:41:28,949
I'LL HAVE TO ASK YOU
TO COME BACK IN THE MORNING.

553
00:41:28,949 --> 00:41:32,902
I'VE COME A LONG WAY,
AND I KNOW HE WANTS TO SEE ME,
SO WHAT DO YOU SAY ?

554
00:41:32,902 --> 00:41:36,723
I'M SORRY, REALLY.
IT'S HOSPITAL POLICY.

555
00:41:48,918 --> 00:41:51,254
[ Mulder Screaming ]
HELP !

556
00:41:52,672 --> 00:41:56,059
- HELP !
- [ Creature Screeching ]

557
00:42:15,261 --> 00:42:18,515
[ Skinner ]
AGENT SCULLY, I HAVE TO SAY
I'M AT A BIT OF A LOSS HERE.

558
00:42:18,515 --> 00:42:22,802
DO I INFER CORRECTLY
FROM THIS THAT YOU BELIEVE
THERE'S SOME...

559
00:42:22,802 --> 00:42:25,305
MERIT TO
AGENT MULDER'S CLAIMS ?

560
00:42:27,807 --> 00:42:30,810
I BELIEVE THAT AGENT MULDER
IS MENTALLY SOUND...

561
00:42:30,810 --> 00:42:33,813
AND FIT FOR DUTY.

562
00:42:33,813 --> 00:42:36,316
ASIDE FROM THAT BELIEF,
I CAN ONLY PRESENT TO YOU...

563
00:42:36,316 --> 00:42:38,685
THE FEW HARD FACTS THAT
I'VE BEEN ABLE TO GATHER--

564
00:42:38,685 --> 00:42:42,622
THAT, AS PER
AGENT MULDER'S ASSERTIONS,

565
00:42:42,622 --> 00:42:46,076
A TOXIN HAS BEEN FOUND
TO HAVE BEEN INJECTED
INTO THE SPINE...

566
00:42:46,076 --> 00:42:47,961
OF THE SHOOTING VICTIM,
MARK BACKUS.

567
00:42:47,961 --> 00:42:51,798
AS OF YET,
WE'VE BEEN UNABLE
TO IDENTIFY IT.

568
00:42:51,798 --> 00:42:53,717
FURTHERMORE,

569
00:42:54,217 --> 00:42:57,220
GREGORY PINCUS HAS
APPARENTLY DISAPPEARED
WITHOUT A TRACE,

570
00:42:57,220 --> 00:43:00,223
ALONG WITH HALF A DOZEN
OTHER KEY WITNESSES...

571
00:43:00,724 --> 00:43:02,726
INTEGRAL TO
THIS INVESTIGATION,

572
00:43:03,226 --> 00:43:05,228
AMONG THEM AGENT MULDER'S
NURSE AT THE HOSPITAL...

573
00:43:05,228 --> 00:43:07,597
AND SEVERAL
OF VINYLRIGHT EMPLOYEES.

574
00:43:07,597 --> 00:43:10,483
MEN AND WOMEN DESCRIBED
BY MULDER AS ZOMBIES.

575
00:43:14,821 --> 00:43:16,322
[ Sighs ]

576
00:43:16,823 --> 00:43:19,826
I PERSONALLY CAN VOUCH
FOR THE FACT THAT...

577
00:43:19,826 --> 00:43:22,829
THERE WAS AN INTRUDER
IN AGENT MULDER'S
HOSPITAL ROOM.

578
00:43:22,829 --> 00:43:25,949
DESCRIBE THIS INTRUDER.

579
00:43:29,452 --> 00:43:31,287
IT WAS DARK.

580
00:43:31,287 --> 00:43:33,757
YOU MUST'VE GOTTEN A GLIMPSE.
WHAT DID YOU SEE ?

581
00:43:45,502 --> 00:43:48,004
WHAT DID YOU TELL HIM ?

582
00:43:48,505 --> 00:43:52,008
THE TRUTH, AS WELL AS
I UNDERSTAND IT.

583
00:43:52,008 --> 00:43:54,511
[ Bell Dings ]
WHICH IS ?

584
00:44:00,016 --> 00:44:01,518
FOLIE A DEUX--

585
00:44:02,018 --> 00:44:04,521
A MADNESS
SHARED BY TWO.

586
00:44:06,523 --> 00:44:08,892
[ Many Voices Speaking
  At Once ]

587
00:44:22,405 --> 00:44:25,408
MR. JACOX, LET ME TAKE
A FEW MOMENTS TO TELL YOU...

588
00:44:25,408 --> 00:44:28,912
ABOUT THE ADVANTAGES
OF WEATHERRIGHT
REPLACEMENT WINDOWS.

589
00:44:28,912 --> 00:44:31,915
THEY KEEP DOWN HIGH HEATING
AND COOLING COSTS.

590
00:44:31,915 --> 00:44:35,418
THEY BEAUTIFY--

591
00:44:35,418 --> 00:44:38,421
THEY BEAUTIFY AND ADD VALUE
TO YOUR HOME AS WELL AS--
[ Fluttering ]

592
00:44:40,423 --> 00:44:42,792
MR. JACOX !

593
00:44:42,792 --> 00:44:45,245
[ Whispering ]
IT'S HERE !

594
00:45:25,317 --> 00:45:27,887
[ Child ]
I MADE THIS !

